title: Pumpkin cake with cream cheese frosting
ingredients: ['4 eggs', '330g caster sugar', '250ml vegetable oil', '425g pumpkin puree', '250g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '175g cream cheese', '90g butter, softened', '360g icing sugar']
